<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Voxera Health</title>

<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
  background: #0f172a;
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
}

header {
  padding: 60px 20px;
}

h1 {
  font-size: 48px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.tagline {
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #38bdf8;
}

.section {
  padding: 40px 20px;
}

.card {
  background: #1e293b;
  margin: 20px auto;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  max-width: 400px;
}

footer {
  padding: 20px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #94a3b8;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>Voxera Health</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Voice. Data. Care.</p>
</header>

<div class="section">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Assistive Communication</h2>
    <p>Advanced AAC devices empowering patient voice.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Cloud Platform</h2>
    <p>Secure patient data and therapy tools in one place.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Care Integration</h2>
    <p>Connecting therapists, patients, and families.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  © 2026 Voxera Health
</footer>

</body>
</html>
